snippet.title: Gunborg demo trailer
snippet.description:
A trailer for the indie game Gunborg. Demo available at https://ricpau.itch.io/gunborg

Here's a list of all the music tracks used in the game so far:
For Champions of The Future - ihsandincer
Glitched Out - Taco Music
Darkness in Metropolis - Sascha Giebel
High Jump - Evgeny Kiselevich
Neon Roads - Infraction
Disco Daft - Infraction
The Assault - SnowMusicStudio
Black invasion - SnowMusicStudio
Drums of War - Amit Harel
Ocean motion - Alex Grey
Crime in the streets - Diva Production
Alien Design - Yoav Alyagon
Epic Intense Trailer Intro Indent - Jon Wright
Apocalypse Beginning - AleXZavesa
No Time To Waste - SPMusicGroup
Future Swag - Alistair Fernandes
